name: 扎克·普里莫
introduction: Zach Primo is an Actor born and raised in New Orleans, Louisiana. He is known for his work in Leverage: Redemption (2022) and Killing It (2022). He is often referred to as a young Matthew McConaughey. He found a love for acting at a very young age and began to pursue the career at 15 years old ; and will now be spending time in Los Angeles taking classes and improving his skill set as an actor. He loves sports and played quarterback and receiver for his local football team until the 10th grade. He is also passionate about fitness and nutrition and is a personal trainer, certified by the National Academy of Sports Medicine (NASM). He is also a bit of a history buff, as well as loves to play guitar in his spare time. He also loves modeling and has done so in print catalogs and has walked runways ; featuring up and coming designers, as well as local brands.
